original_title: Bring It On: A Tribute to Broadway
overview: Based on the 2013 Tony Award Nominated Musical 'Bring It On!' Libretto by Jeff Whitty, Music by Lin-Manuel Miranda and Tom Kitt, Lyrics by Amanda Green and Lin-Manuel Miranda with additional Brand New Musical Number comes an all fan made tribute musical spectacular!  [Film was issued a Cease and Desist by Universal NBC Spring 2014]  ***Film Never Released***
title: Bring It On: A Tribute to Broadway
